ProjectStatus is a BusinessClass
    owned by Projects
    prefix is STS
    classic name is ACSTATUS

    Ontology
        symbolic key is ProjectStatus
            classic set name is STSSET1
            classic name is USR-STATUS

    Patterns
        implements StaticJava

    Persistent Fields

        Description  
        Billable                is Boolean
            classic name is BILLABLE-FLAG
            default label is "Billing"
        AllowRevenueRecognition is Boolean
            classic name is REV-REC-FLAG
            default label is "Revenue"
        AllowCapitalization     is Boolean
            classic name is CAPITAL-FLAG
            default label is "Capitalization"
        AllowPurge              is Boolean
            classic name is PURGE-FLAG
            default label is "Purge"

    Field Rules

        Description
            required

		AllowPurge
			if 	(AllowPurge)
				constraint (!Billable
					and 	!AllowRevenueRecognition
					and		!AllowCapitalization)
						"CannotSelectPurgeWithOtherFunctionsSelected"            

    Actions
        Create is a Create Action

        Update is an Update Action

        Delete is a Delete Action
